    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Photographic prints in which bromoil print matrices are used to transfer the image to another support. Normally the matrix would reveal the final image of a bromoil print. Bromoil transfer prints have the ability to be rendered on any support, not just the specially prepared silver gelatin paper of the matrix as in a bromoil print.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
